Program: Outlook
Title: Cult Suicides in Uganda
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrbp
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
An assessment of the mass suicide by cult church members in South West Uganda. Jamaican actor Carl Bradshaw talks about his new film, 'Third World Cop'. Shock art in China involving animals, real blood and human body parts. Finally, hot air ballooning. Presented by Fred Dove.